# Workstation Provision

- Read `AGENTS.md` and `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` before substantial edits.
- Keep Ansible tasks idempotent.
- Use existing role defaults instead of hardcoded values.
- Do not add secrets, tokens or private keys.
- Validate with `make check`.
- Run `make lint` when the tools are available.

